  "notes": [
    {
      "id": "note1",
      "position": {"x": 100, "y": 50},
      "text": "FARMASSIST+ VERTICAL FARM KIT (V1)\nNFT Hydroponic System for Lettuce\nMCU: ESP32-DevKitC-32E\nArchitecture: Bun + Hono + Prisma + MQTT\nGCD4F 2026 Competition"
    },
    {
      "id": "note2",
      "position": {"x": 100, "y": 600},
      "text": "POWER NOTES:\n- Main: 12V 5A AC/DC adapter (grid)\n- Buck converter: 12V → 5V @ 3A\n- ESP32 3.3V onboard regulator\n- Total draw: ~2.8A @ 12V\n- Battery backup optional for demos"
    },
    {
      "id": "note3",
      "position": {"x": 300, "y": 600},
      "text": "I2C BUS DEVICES:\n- BH1750 Light Sensor (0x23)\n- DS3231 RTC Module (0x68)\n- SDA: GPIO21 (4.7K pull-up)\n- SCL: GPIO22 (4.7K pull-up)"
    },
    {
      "id": "note4",
      "position": {"x": 500, "y": 600},
      "text": "MQTT TOPICS:\nPublish: farmassist/{user_id}/farm_vertical_004/ARD_V001_001/telemetry\nSubscribe: farmassist/{user_id}/farm_vertical_004/ARD_V001_001/cmd\nPublish Interval: 20 seconds (faster for hydroponics)\nBroker: localhost:1883 (dev)"
    },
    {
      "id": "note5",
      "position": {"x": 700, "y": 600},
      "text": "SAFETY FEATURES:\n- Water level < 5cm → Auto pump shutoff\n- pH < 5.5 or > 7.0 → Buzzer alert\n- DO < 4 mg/L → Critical alert\n- Temp > 30°C → Cooling notification\n- All logged to TimescaleDB"
    },
    {
      "id": "note6",
      "position": {"x": 100, "y": 700},
      "text": "CALIBRATION:\n- Water pH: pH 4.0, 7.0, 10.0 buffers\n- TDS: 1413 µS/cm solution @ 25°C\n- DO: 0% (sodium sulfite), 100% (air-saturated)\n- Water temp: Ice bath (0°C), Boiling (100°C)\n- Ultrasonic: Known distances"
    },
    {
      "id": "note7",
      "position": {"x": 300, "y": 700},
      "text": "OPTIMAL LETTUCE RANGES:\n- pH: 5.5-6.5\n- EC: 1.2-2.0 mS/cm (840-1400 ppm)\n- Water Temp: 18-22°C\n- Air Temp: 16-24°C\n- DO: >5 mg/L\n- Light: 200-400 µmol/m²/s (12-16h/day)"
    },
    {
      "id": "note8",
      "position": {"x": 500, "y": 700},
      "text": "VOLTAGE DIVIDER FOR HC-SR04 ECHO:\nESP32 GPIO13 is 3.3V tolerant\nHC-SR04 ECHO outputs 5V\nUse 1KΩ + 2KΩ divider:\n5V → 1KΩ → GPIO13 → 2KΩ → GND\nOutput: 5V * (2K/(1K+2K)) = 3.33V"
    }
  ],
